channel.title: 200 BPM Collab Thing
channel.description: I was recently making this weird 200 BPM song with a precision arp that goes all the way up and down the scale with the new update, and decided I could make it into a collab song, after how fun it was to make one before this. So basically just make a little section of really whatever. I'm excited to see (if anyone joins) how this might turn out! Here's a link to the project: https://app.auxy.co/projects/n3LKUqeQl5KkpiuaucPTtQ== If you decide to add something, just post the link in this topic, and I'll check it out!
